{
  "stem": "10905.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a very sick kid next door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was allowed to go out from our barrack, our compound, to-- into the Dutch compound with my father.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know or didn't believe that there were gas chambers in Bergen-Belsen, that they were not gassing people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were sure they were not gassing people when we were there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the reason for it is because being as young as I was, I could go and take showers either with my mother or my father.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And each time when my father went, I took showers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when the women went, I'd go along with my mother to take showers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, I had-- had the slightest inkling that-- that not water was going to come out of those shower heads, I'm sure I would not [? do it ?].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You'd get assembled together, and then you'd march maybe five, six miles away.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there you would undress-- just like they did in other places where they gassed the people, except here there was no gas.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you're saying that if you had heard that, you would have been afraid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Had my-- not, not I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Had my parents and anybody heard that this was going on, they surely would not have exposed their child to go through it twice a month.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, just on a-- that today they're going to gas people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So nobody had an inkling or thought that they were gassing people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "See, we-- we were special.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The others had their uniforms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had no uniforms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We wore--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All different compounds.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All different, had just like-- like-- we were very, very special, because we were not even supposed to have been there, and-- but we were there.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
